
install pip virtual env -> python3 -m venv env
Activate virtual env -> source env/bin/activate

pytorch installation -- https://pytorch.org/
validate installation - test-installation.py , https://12ft.io/proxy?q=https%3A%2F%2Ftowardsdatascience.com%2Finstalling-pytorch-on-apple-m1-chip-with-gpu-acceleration-3351dc44d67c

Finetuning a pretrained model - https://huggingface.co/docs/transformers/training

Docker create image from app - https://docs.docker.com/language/python/build-images/
1. create a Dockerfile with the steps to perform
2. Run "docker build --tag project-text-generation ." on the terminal from inside the folder

Docker create container from the image
Run "docker run -d -p 80:80 project-text-generation"

############# Setup ML Flow for model tracking
1. pip install mlflow , Then test the installation by running "mlflow ui"

###Deploy the docker image 

